data.description: Brand new roof just installed! Tons of natural light & gleaming hardwood floors, this stunning 1-owner property is being offered for sale for the first time since being built. Relax in the bright & open living spaces or cook & entertain in style with updated shaker cabinetry, a large eat-in island & an easy-flow layout boasting new carpeting! Wander downstairs to the professionally finished basement, complete with a kitchenette/wet bar & plenty of recreation space. Outside, enjoy a fully fenced & landscaped backyard, complete with a covered patio & an XL shed. Clean lines, well-appointed finishes & a fantastic location within walking distance to the neighborhood park, situated in an established neighborhood in the top rated Hilliard school district!
